<section class="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>We are a non-profit organization dedicated to providing shelter, care, and love to abandoned and neglected animals in Bulgaria. Our mission is to rescue these animals, provide them with the medical attention they need, and find them loving forever homes.</p>
</section>

